rows.label: qev011002_MSG0005
rows.name:
...I see. No, I...
I knew that was the reality when we left him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011002_MSG0006
rows.name:
Look, could I ask you to bring his body back?
We'd all like to give him a proper funeral.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011002_MSG0007
rows.name:
I know it's asking a lot, but if there's anything of his
you can find there...I figure the team would want to
have something to remember him by.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011002_MSG0008
rows.name:
Sorry to put all this on you. I know Law would've
appreciated it.[ST:wait ]
